{"tid":1964654,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[支那有自由?] 武漢解封 武漢人：沒有外界想像的恢復行動自由","createTime":"2020-04-09T03:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T05:10:08.000Z","uid":176401,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d3ec407b6f8c37d62e2904cd1e1c1f879f7c5381","tid":1964654,"uid":176401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T03:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m1.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2020/0409/20200409083349836.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm1.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2020%2F0409%2F20200409083349836.jpg&h=da58e6c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武漢解封日，上班族全幅武裝上工。<br />\n<br />\n封城76天之後，中國武漢終於在4月8日解封，而在解封日凌晨，即有數萬武漢人漏夜出逃外地，今天的武漢市容，車輛流動增加，但是，據留在當地的武漢人卻指，並沒有外界想像的恢復行動自由，心理還是很害怕，覺得困境及危機並沒有解除，還是要小心謹慎的過日子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://m1.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2020/0409/20200409083350128.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm1.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2020%2F0409%2F20200409083350128.jpg&h=c454b996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武漢解封后，市街上衣着變化多。<br />\n<br />\n《德國之聲》報導，武漢當地居民表示，解封只是得到復工許可的人員可以流動，這些人需要健康碼「綠碼」及政府認可的復工證明，才可以從住家的小區離開，一般人還是不自由的，只能待在家裡，市面上大部分商店都沒有開業，開店的大致就三種店包括大超市、藥店、網信，市面上的人潮也不多。<br />\n<br />\n昨天搭公車上班的一位先生表示，看到大部分人都全副武裝上車，包括護目鏡、防毒面具、拋棄式雨衣跟手套，還有人用塑膠袋包住手機&hellip;，彼此之間乎不交談，全車都很安靜，且解封首日，公車及地鐵都沒有滿載。<br />\n<br />\n也有武漢民眾覺得，封城封久了，都有點麻木了，早能出去的早就跑了，不能出去的也都習慣封城步調，經過2個多月的封城，很多人的經濟都受到重擊，有些本來有一餐沒一餐的人，現在更慘了，但是，他們沒有在臉上透露困窘，而是裝着很幸福，讓人更覺得心酸。<br />\n<br />\n即時解封，一位小姐說，本來想去看牙醫、剪個頭髮或買個花，但只是想想，覺得避免風險還是算了，還是小心過日子。可能不少武漢人都跟她有相同的想法，大要很長一段時間才能真正恢復。<br />\n<br />\n本文網址：<a href=\"https://hk.aboluowang.com/2020/0409/1434233.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.aboluowang.com%2F2020%2F0409%2F1434233.html&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbi%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=40b3860f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.aboluowang.com/2020/0409/1434233.html</a>"},{"pid":"ce75b0bb4eb3ba9c11678bc3264f69a2c507567e","tid":1964654,"uid":123738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T03:56:36.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦支那狗，總之要開工就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5128717d029259627a57f674240e91de3cad0c5e","tid":1964654,"uid":176401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce75b0bb4eb3ba9c11678bc3264f69a2c507567e","tid":1964654,"uid":123738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T03:56:36.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦支那狗，總之要開工就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T04:10:11.000Z","msg":"支那蝗命就是賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8970629929ad3fd99796899ac16c186314dcb9","tid":1964654,"uid":249924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T04:12:09.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩 我只係擔心d支那狗黎播毒屌你老母"},{"pid":"b2d74cbfd8c611c78b51b730cc5f669128e01357","tid":1964654,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T04:17:06.000Z","msg":"死咁多人<br />\n<br />\n就咁就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a357b5a84a845ef9ada273d1fc440e2d2307e24","tid":1964654,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2d74cbfd8c611c78b51b730cc5f669128e01357","tid":1964654,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T04:17:06.000Z","msg":"死咁多人<br />\n<br />\n就咁就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T04:19:16.000Z","msg":"死太少人，仲未去到暴動地步 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c79a47b113a1af6c5e9a11364ae4b0636f0e831","tid":1964654,"uid":238415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T04:22:01.000Z","msg":"其實仲呼吸緊仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif